Parameters.Parameter: ▉ Water ▉ Forest ▉ Grass

Datasource.Parameter: (SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE landuse IN ('residential', 'commercial', 'retail')) AS data
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE aeroway IN ('aerodrome') OR landuse IN ('industrial')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "leisure" IN ('park', 'playground', 'pitch', 'golf_course') OR landuse IN ('recreation_ground', 'grass', 'cemetery')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('wood', 'scrub') OR landuse IN ('forest')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('wetland')) AS data
(SELECT way, waterway AS type, name FROM planet_osm_line WHERE waterway IN ('river', 'canal', 'stream', 'ditch') AND tunnel IS NULL AND (layer NOT IN ('-1', '-2') OR layer IS NULL)) as DATA

(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('water', 'pond') OR waterway IN ('basin', 'canal', 'mill_pond', 'pond', 'riverbank', 'stream') OR landuse IN ('reservoir', 'basin')) AS data
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE route IN ('ferry') ) as DATA
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('glacier')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE landuse IN ('military') OR military IN ('danger_area')) AS data
( SELECT DISTINCT ON(way) way, name FROM planet_osm_line WHERE boundary = 'administrative' AND admin_level = '2' ORDER BY way ) AS data
( SELECT way, "building" AS type, way_area AS area FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE building NOT IN ('0','false', 'no') ORDER BY ST_YMin(ST_Envelope(way)) DESC ) AS data

(SELECT way, highway AS type, name, tracktype, tunnel, bridge, oneway, z_order, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link', 'trunk', 'trunk_link', 'primary', 'primary_link', 'secondary', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1'))) AND tunnel IN('yes') ORDER BY z_order ) as DATA
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE aeroway IN ('taxiway') ) as DATA
(SELECT way, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length FROM planet_osm_line WHERE aeroway IN ('runway') ) as DATA

(SELECT way, bicycle, CASE WHEN "mtb:scale"~E'^\\d+$' THEN "mtb:scale"::integer ELSE NULL END as mtbscale FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway IN ('path', 'footway', 'steps', 'bridleway') AND (bicycle IS NULL OR bicycle NOT IN('designated')) ) as DATA

(SELECT way, ST_Perimeter(way)::integer as boundary FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE barrier IN ('fence') AND (ST_Perimeter(way)::integer > 400) UNION SELECT way, ST_Perimeter(way)::integer as boundary FROM planet_osm_line WHERE barrier IN ('fence') AND (ST_Length(way)::integer > 400) ) AS data

(SELECT way, highway AS type, name, tunnel, bridge, tracktype, oneway, z_order, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, CASE WHEN highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link') OR (highway IN('trunk') AND oneway IN ('yes')) THEN 90 WHEN highway IN ('trunk', 'trunk_link') THEN 100 WHEN highway IN ('primary', 'primary_link') THEN 60 WHEN highway IN ('secondary', 'secondary_link') THEN 50 WHEN highway IN ('tertiary', 'tertiary_link') THEN 40 WHEN highway IN ('road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1')) THEN 30 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link', 'trunk', 'trunk_link', 'primary', 'primary_link', 'secondary', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1'))) AND (bridge IS NULL OR bridge NOT IN('yes')) ORDER BY prio DESC ) as DATA
(SELECT way, highway AS type, tracktype, bicycle FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway IN ('track') AND (tracktype IS NULL OR tracktype <> 'grade1') ) as DATA

( SELECT way, tunnel, railway as type FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (railway NOT IN ('abandoned', 'disused', 'razed', 'platform', 'construction')) AND (service IS NULL OR service NOT IN('yard')) ) as DATA

(SELECT way, highway AS type, name, tracktype, tunnel, bridge, oneway, z_order, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, CASE WHEN highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link') OR (highway IN('trunk') AND oneway IN ('yes')) THEN 90 WHEN highway IN ('trunk', 'trunk_link') THEN 100 WHEN highway IN ('primary', 'primary_link') THEN 60 WHEN highway IN ('secondary', 'secondary_link') THEN 50 WHEN highway IN ('tertiary', 'tertiary_link') THEN 40 WHEN highway IN ('road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1')) THEN 30 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link', 'trunk', 'trunk_link', 'primary', 'primary_link', 'secondary', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1'))) AND bridge IN('yes') AND (layer IS NULL OR layer <= '1') ORDER BY prio DESC ) as DATA

(SELECT way, highway AS type, name, tracktype, tunnel, bridge, oneway, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length, CASE WHEN highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link') OR (highway IN('trunk') AND oneway IN ('yes')) THEN 90 WHEN highway IN ('trunk', 'trunk_link') THEN 100 WHEN highway IN ('primary', 'primary_link') THEN 60 WHEN highway IN ('secondary', 'secondary_link') THEN 50 WHEN highway IN ('tertiary', 'tertiary_link') THEN 40 WHEN highway IN ('road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1')) THEN 30 ELSE 0 END as prio FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'motorway_link', 'trunk', 'trunk_link', 'primary', 'primary_link', 'secondary', 'secondary_link', 'tertiary', 'tertiary_link', 'road', 'unclassified', 'residential', 'pedestrian', 'living_street', 'service') OR (highway IN ('track') AND tracktype IN ('grade1'))) AND bridge IN('yes') AND (layer >= '2') ORDER BY prio DESC ) as DATA
(SELECT ST_LineMerge(ST_Union(way)) as way, ref from planet_osm_line WHERE route='bicycle' group by ref) as data
( --SELECT way from planet_osm_line --WHERE route='bicycle' SELECT * FROM cycleroutes ) as data
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE highway IN ('cycleway') OR bicycle IN('designated') ) as DATA
(SELECT way, name, aerialway as type FROM planet_osm_line WHERE aerialway IN ('cable_car', 'chairlift', 'gondola', 'chair_lift', 'mixed_lift', 'goods') ) as DATA
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_line WHERE power IN ('line', 'minor_line') ) as DATA

(SELECT way, highway AS type, ref, CHAR_LENGTH(ref) AS reflen FROM planet_osm_line WHERE (highway IN ('motorway', 'trunk', 'primary')) AND (bridge IS NULL OR bridge NOT IN('yes')) AND ref IS NOT NULL) as DATA
(SELECT way, ref FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "highway" IN ('motorway_junction') ) as data

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, name, ele, CASE WHEN tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel') THEN tourism ELSE amenity END as type FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 300) as snapped, way, name, ele, amenity, tourism FROM planet_osm_point WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel')) UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 300) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way, name, ele, amenity, tourism FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel')) ) as tmp ) as data

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, name, ele, CASE WHEN tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel') THEN tourism ELSE amenity END as type FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 500) as snapped, way, name, ele, tourism, amenity FROM planet_osm_point WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel')) UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 500) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way, name, ele, tourism, amenity FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut', 'hotel')) ) as tmp ) as data

( SELECT way, name, ele FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut')) UNION SELECT way, name, ele FROM planet_osm_point WHERE (amenity IN ('pub','fast_food','restaurant','bar','biergarten')) OR (tourism IN ('alpine_hut')) ) as data
( SELECT way FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE amenity IN ('shelter') UNION SELECT way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE amenity IN ('shelter') ) as data
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE power IN ('tower', 'station', 'sub_station') ) as DATA
( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way),50) as way, name, railway as type, subway FROM planet_osm_point WHERE railway IN ('station', 'halt', 'tram_stop') ) as DATA

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 200) as snapped, way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE amenity='parking' UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 200) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE amenity='parking' ) as tmp ) as data
(SELECT way, name, ele FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "natural" IN ('peak')) as DATA
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "leisure" IN ('park', 'playground', 'pitch', 'golf_course') OR landuse IN ('recreation_ground', 'grass', 'cemetery')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('wetland')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('wood', 'scrub') OR landuse IN ('forest')) AS data

(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name, ele FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('water', 'pond') OR waterway IN ('basin', 'canal', 'mill_pond', 'pond', 'riverbank', 'stream') OR landuse IN ('reservoir', 'basin')) AS data

(select way, name, st_length(st_transform(way,4326)::geography)::integer as length from planet_osm_line where waterway IN ('river', 'canal', 'stream', 'ditch') AND tunnel IS NULL AND (layer NOT IN ('-1', '-2') OR layer IS NULL) AND name IS NOT NULL ) as data
( SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE "natural" IN ('glacier') AND name IS NOT NULL ) AS data
(SELECT ST_LineMerge(ST_Union(way)) as way, route_name from planet_osm_line WHERE route='bicycle' AND route_name IS NOT NULL group by route_name) as data
(SELECT way, route_name from planet_osm_line WHERE route='bicycle' AND route_name IS NOT NULL) as data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE aeroway IN ('aerodrome') OR landuse IN ('industrial')) AS data
(SELECT way, way_area AS area, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE landuse IN ('military') OR military IN ('danger_area')) AS data

( SELECT DISTINCT ON(snapped) way, CASE WHEN leisure = 'playground' THEN leisure ELSE tourism END as type, name FROM ( SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(way, 200) as snapped, way, tourism, leisure, name FROM planet_osm_point WHERE tourism IN ('viewpoint', 'information', 'zoo', 'aquarium') OR leisure = 'playground' UNION SELECT ST_SnapToGrid(ST_Centroid(way), 200) as snapped, ST_Centroid(way) as way, tourism, leisure, name FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE tourism IN ('viewpoint', 'information', 'zoo', 'aquarium') OR leisure = 'playground' ) as tmp ) as data
( SELECT way, shop as type FROM planet_osm_polygon WHERE shop IN ('bicycle', 'supermarket') UNION SELECT way, shop as type FROM planet_osm_point WHERE shop IN ('bicycle', 'supermarket') ) as data

(SELECT way, name, ele, place, CASE WHEN population ~E'^\\d+$' THEN population::integer ELSE NULL END as pop FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "place" IN ('city', 'town', 'village', 'hamlet', 'suburb') AND name IS NOT NULL) as DATA

( SELECT way, capital, ele, CHAR_LENGTH(name) AS strlen, CASE WHEN population ~E'^\\d+$' THEN population::integer ELSE NULL END as pop, CASE WHEN int_name IS NOT NULL THEN int_name ELSE name END as name FROM planet_osm_point WHERE place = 'city' AND name IS NOT NULL AND (CASE WHEN population ~E'^\\d+$' THEN population::integer ELSE NULL END) > 500000 ORDER BY pop DESC LIMIT 400 ) AS data
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "man_made" IN ('mast', 'tower', 'communications_tower', 'antenna') ) as data
(SELECT way FROM planet_osm_point WHERE "amenity" IN ('place_of_worship') AND "religion" IN ('christian') ) as data
